{"tid":1830481,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黑警：開鎖你部電話 否認懷疑你偷野將你拘捕","createTime":"2020-01-19T15:41:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-19T22:21:18.000Z","uid":22556,"like":183,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":75,"replies":[{"pid":"351c2e5055a5e20644bc0519c5c83696c770d63d","tid":1830481,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T15:41:30.000Z","msg":"在畢打街，至少6男1女被截查後遭拘捕，離開前需被警員以攝錄機拍下樣貌。其中1名被捕男子疑因不適嘔吐，有急救員想上前協助，惟被警員拒絕。大部分人截查後獲放行，包括許智峯及吳兆康。吳兆康指，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">警員曾粗暴將他撞向牆邊，又用粗言穢語要求吳解鎖其手機，稱「懷疑手機偷返嚟」，若不解鎖則會作出拘捕。</span></span></span></strong>當時吳曾以攝錄機錄影，但再被警員威脅，若不再停止錄影會作出拘捕。吳離開前向防暴警員索取警察編號，並再要求警員解釋截查原因。在場警員則拒絕解釋，指吳兆康「破壞社會安寧」，又謂「作為議員一啲法律知識都冇，我都好失望。」、「唔好同佢講，講完佢都唔明」。<br />\n<br />\n吳兆康對此大表不滿：「鄧炳強係咪講大話？又話警員唔會講粗言穢語！」<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">吳又指曾致電警方傳媒聯絡，質詢現場警員的行為，但傳媒聯絡隊卻「卸膊」指「無能為力，係前線嘅決定」。</span></span></strong> 他質疑警方今日截查行為不當，指警員從來未試過向議員作出截查的要求，並斥「係警民關係科失職 」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1070087\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1070087&d=3W3ENIgnTPsh0%2B1doSs%2BP%2F3Ut%2FTlF5atQuTXJDR4vuI%3D&h=cc78d1f5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1070087&h=43b45a5f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1070087</a>"},{"pid":"ec5bebf26c7263e93e6637bafe77a558e6eefe40","tid":1830481,"uid":88743,"like":153,"dislike":0,"score":153,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T15:43:28.000Z","msg":"我都懷疑黑警張委任證係貪返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c42c86a99a63e73bbbb0e1e73a73117d0346a180","tid":1830481,"uid":313203,"like":153,"dislike":0,"score":153,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T15:45:01.000Z","msg":"極度懷疑黑警套裝偷返黎，唔係點會冇委任證"},{"pid":"dd380ae8755f7adab617959bc242364f4ee99e71","tid":1830481,"uid":266672,"like":57,"dislike":2,"score":55,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T15:45:22.000Z","msg":"原來警曱有法律知識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"402d68f6bffa020a8f3f3f5d6cf4278649865063","tid":1830481,"uid":278765,"like":63,"dislike":0,"score":63,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T15:47:15.000Z","msg":"popo 點證明自己著緊條底褲, 唔係偷番嚟!?!?!?"},{"pid":"5beab09b9f25e0ce85a2be4e4c5d919ce3b40198","tid":1830481,"uid":101307,"like":113,"dislike":3,"score":110,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T15:48:42.000Z","msg":"Medical ID<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有就lockscreen開比佢睇 然後就唔駛解鎖 反正都玩野要拉 係拉就快手<br />\n佢要玩野你解完鎖佢都係會拉你 倒不如證明完個機係自己之後就由佢鳩up 過程中最好錄低佢講過咩 第日用作呈堂證供<br />\n憑咩要聽個讀唔成書既人講野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大大聲聲屌佢都得啦 得連登仔先會驚呢樣驚嗰樣"},{"pid":"2c79554925be81e94ce7216027719bde48047fd9","tid":1830481,"uid":65887,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T15:49:01.000Z","msg":"唔好淨係得個講字<br />\n作為議員, 應該正式去投訴, 去信警務處處長要求交代<br />\n定期開記者會跟進事件"},{"pid":"aaf4d6f2e9f9a274db23fb539f264f03d153ccf5","tid":1830481,"uid":7168,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T15:51:22.000Z","msg":"依部電話係我既 麻煩你寫落口供<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其他我冇野講<br />\n<br />\n不過癲狗真係冇撚得同佢玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 出得黎預左48<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n黑警死全家"},{"pid":"fdebe7661d0d428290da7bf156ed1bad305d09c7","tid":1830481,"uid":94184,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T15:52:40.000Z","msg"