.net/node/1070087</a>"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T15:58:26.000Z","msg":"其實wallpaper 整張係有自己名 自己電話號碼嘅又有冇得諗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T17:41:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">去示威就唔好拎常用電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"f29eb3a0c620fcb60853aee123ccfe0f483b2647","tid":1830481,"uid":325757,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2c79554925be81e94ce7216027719bde48047fd9","tid":1830481,"uid":65887,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T15:49:01.000Z","msg":"唔好淨係得個講字<br />\n作為議員, 應該正式去投訴, 去信警務處處長要求交代<br />\n定期開記者會跟進事件"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T17:41:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仆街 俾人影咗樣 佢哋會唔會有事<br />\n聽聞彥林同鄭文傑都係咁俾人影低點相出咗事"},{"pid":"fdf969b79112eb635485a30df292f0d240251b50","tid":1830481,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"b4d14d229e2b89ebbb0b26a29e00b657c5284300","tid":1830481,"uid":76365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T17:40:02.000Z","msg":"認真，遇到呢啲情況要點處理？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T17:41:51.000Z","msg":"冇,佢係特登玩鳩你<br />\n你駁嘴立即打鳩你<br />\n只可以乖乖地解鎖比佢睇"},{"pid":"b36740e54e8afc787971ec2a85787724db723aec","tid":1830481,"uid":114994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T17:41:52.000Z","msg":"好簡單 佢懷疑就懷疑<br />\n部手機係你一定告唔入"},{"pid":"5a80b6a98292bcd59d2c4af950e1c2eea5a6f32b","tid":1830481,"uid":46576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T17:43:42.000Z","msg":"無罪推定呢？"},{"pid":"5ee8db214b7a2c5868f735393e66c21fc2224f95","tid":1830481,"uid":282494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T17:46:26.000Z","msg":"警暴問題好嚴重"},{"pid":"51fe27c2141655335884ff52b838a461e63a1b10","tid":1830481,"uid":90601,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"